Introduction

Zhang Shuaibo is a Chinese singer under Well Entertainment.

He was first known for being a contestant in the survival show Youth With You 3, where he ranked 100th place and was eliminated.

In 2023, he was a contestant in MNET' survival show Boys Planet, where he was also eliminated after ranking 28th place this time.

He was a contestant in SBS' survival show Universe League, where his team, the "Team Rhythm", won the prism cup, securing him a spot as a member of the final group AHOF.
